As they approached Baron Blankslate’s lair, the villain cackled. “You cannot defeat the power of neutrality!” he sneered, launching a wave of paperwork and office memos at them.

But the LFD was prepared! Captain Crayon drew a portal through which all the paperwork vanished. The Shady Artist sketched an illusion so dazzling that Baron Blankslate tripped over his own shoelaces. Professor Puddle splashed vibrant hues across the walls, and Glitterbomb unleashed a magnificent explosion of sparkles that made everything shimmer like a disco ball.

